no toy shit.

06:54.440 --> 06:56.591
Course you're not.

06:56.760 --> 06:59.116
So, you like it?

06:59.280 --> 07:01.511
I love it.

07:01.680 --> 07:03.876
Made it down to the Keys
in record time.

07:04.040 --> 07:06.430
Checked out my boat.
You oughta see it.

07:06.600 --> 07:08.273
30-footer, twin Mercs,

07:08.440 --> 07:11.000
