the good things in my life.

07:24.920 --> 07:26.957
Took off when you asked
for my help.

07:29.880 --> 07:31.473
So now what?

07:31.680 --> 07:33.911
Well, I'm here to do
what needs to be done,

07:34.080 --> 07:35.719
only I gotta get paid.

07:35.880 --> 07:38.315
And the Roman Godfrey
gravy rain has been derailed.

07:38.520 --> 07:40.318
They owe you any back pay?

07:41.760 --> 07:43.194
Any other clients?

07:43.400 --> 07:44.993
Nada.

07:45.160 --> 07:47.072
I guess I could always start
selling my blood.

07:47.240 --> 07:49.960
No, no, no.
That would be a sinful waste.

07:50.120 --> 07:52.316
Isaac and Olivia's
lemonade stand?

07:54.760 --> 07:56.558
