terrified by her powers.

08:29.880 --> 08:32.349
It doesn't take a clairvoyant to
know something's wrong if you...

08:32.520 --> 08:34.591
Our hands are clean!

08:34.760 --> 08:37.195
So I don't give a jumping fuck
what she turns up.

08:39.120 --> 08:40.839
Bajram?

08:42.600 --> 08:44.273
Sophia and Destiny are close.

08:44.440 --> 08:46.238
Gonna let her go
to the funeral alone?

08:47.720 --> 08:51.600
