11:27.840 --> 11:29.797
Your mother has the LoPS cancer.

11:31.120 --> 11:33.032
She's getting sicker every day.

11:33.200 --> 11:34.919
She will deteriorate

11:35.080 --> 11:36.673
and become hideous.

11:36.880 --> 11:41.511
A monster, really,
or...or more of one.

11:41.720 --> 11:44.519
Judging from the neural plaque
we observed during that autopsy,

11:44.720 --> 11:46.837
her mind will be the first
to go, precipitously,

11:47.000 --> 11:48.832
and the pain...

11:51.720 --> 11:54.554
Let's just say
death will be a relief for her.

11:54.720 --> 11:57.633
- How long?
- A month.

11:57.800 --> 11:59.678
Less.

11:59.840 --> 12:01.672
This disease is Terra nova
for everyone.

12:02.680 --> 12:04.592
- That's one less problem.
- Eventually.

12:04.760 --> 12:07.673
But if you prefer your organs
on the inside of your body,

12:07.840 --> 12:09.513
I would suggest
that you steer clear

12:09.680 --> 12:12.752
