your kind.

12:43.960 --> 12:45.758
Why is no-one here?

12:46.760 --> 12:48.479
People are here.

12:48.640 --> 12:50.597
It was just short notice.

12:50.760 --> 12:52.433
Where are his friends?

13:08.840 --> 13:10.672
Are you ready?

13:27.080 --> 13:28.878
Andreas was a dreamer.

13:31.400 --> 13:34.074
His dream was to make everyone
around him happy...

13:37.000 --> 13:38.957
..especially Destiny...

13:41.160 --> 13:43.356
..who he loved very much.

13:48.520 --> 13:50.352
In their short time together,

13:50.520 --> 13:52.955
he looked after her
and she looked after him.

13:54.440 --> 13:56.113
And all he wanted
was to look after her

13:56.280 --> 13:58.078
for the rest of their lives.

13:59.080 --> 14:00.878
Andreas...

14:02.360 --> 14:04.272
..you were my friend.

14:05.280 --> 14:07.317
You were going to be my family.

14:09.600 --> 14:11.717
I'm so sorry to see you go.

14:15.480 --> 14:17.551
So you just keep pounding
till your hand gets sore

14:17.720 --> 14:19.393
and just when you think
you can't pound anymore,

14:19.560 --> 14:22.678
it goes soft, melts in your
mouth with a sweet, salty taste.

14:22.880 --> 14:24.439
Not in this mouth.

14:24.600 --> 14:27.718
You're gonna change your mind
once you've chowed down on mine

14:27.880 --> 14:30.714
'cause my conch fritters
are the toast of Duval Street.

14:33.400 --> 14:35.039
Hey, what you staring at?

14:35.200 --> 14:38.238
Got a problem with a brown man
kicking it with a white lady?

14:41.920 --> 14:45.550
Didn't think so.

14:45.720 --> 14:48.474
Would you relax?
You're imagining things.

14:48.640 --> 14:52.350
- Why was he staring?
- Because I'm not wearing a bra.

14:56.480 --> 14:58.312
Something wrong?

14:58.480 --> 15:00.437
I mean, with us -
did I do something?

15:00.600 --> 15:04.389
No. I have to work
some things out.

15:15.480 --> 15:17.312
We're gonna get through this.

15:22.440 --> 15:24.875
Um...

15:25.040 --> 15:26.838
Andreas really wanted
to have kids.

15:27.000 --> 15:29.640
He never stopped talking about
the babies.

15:29.800 --> 15:35.034
But...um...kids can be
a real pain, though, too.

15:37.480 --> 15:39.915
He died a hero.
Never forget that.

15:49.080 --> 15:51.231
What do you mean,
he died a hero?

15:53.920 --> 15:58.358
Just that in...the sense
that he was good...

15:59.360 --> 16:00.999
..man - he was a good man.

16:01.160 --> 16:04.039
In a heroic way.

16:05.760 --> 16:09.197
Good... ..man.

16:09.400 --> 16:11.392
It must be beautiful.

16:11.560 --> 16:15.190
It's not about village.
It's about sense of history.

16:15.360 --> 16:17.113
Excuse me.

16:17.280 --> 16:21.354
Hey. Everything alright?

16:21.520 --> 16:24.558
I want to be alone with Andreas.

18:13.440 --> 18:15.193
Ugh!

18:24.320 --> 18:28.234
Please...don't do this.

18:28.400 --> 18:30.039
I'll pay you,
I'll give you whatever.

